            </svg>
            Return to lessons
        </a>
        <h1>Healthy Aging Center</h1>
    </nav>

    <div class="knowledge-container">
        <article class="research-paper">
            <h1>Science of Healthy Aging</h1>

            <div class="article-content">
                <section class="intro-section">
                    <p class="lead-paragraph">
                        Aging well requires understanding biological processes and lifestyle factors. This comprehensive
                        guide covers physical, cognitive, and emotional aspects of aging, evidence-based strategies for
                        longevity, and maintaining quality of life through the decades.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <section class="main-content">
                    <h2>Physical Health Maintenance</h2>
                    <p>
                        Preserve mobility and independence through proactive measures:
                    <ul class="wellness-list">
                        <li>Strength training (2-3x/week)</li>
                        <li>Balance exercises</li>
                        <li>Cardiovascular activity</li>
                        <li>Flexibility routines</li>
                    </ul>
                    Regular health screenings and managing chronic conditions are crucial for successful aging.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Nutrition for Longevity</h2>
                    <p>
                        Optimal aging nutrition focuses on:
                    <ul class="wellness-list">
                        <li>Anti-inflammatory foods</li>
                        <li>Adequate protein intake</li>
                        <li>Micronutrient density</li>
                        <li>Hydration management</li>
                    </ul>
                        Consider Mediterranean or MIND diets, with adjustments for changing metabolic needs.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Cognitive Preservation</h2>
                    <p>
                        Maintain brain health through:
                    <ul class="wellness-list">
                        <li>Continuous learning</li>
                        <li>Social engagement</li>
                        <li>Sleep hygiene</li>
                        <li>Stress reduction techniques</li>
                    </ul>
                    Early detection of cognitive changes through regular mental health checkups.
                    </p>

                    <h2>Preventive Care</h2>
                    <p>
                        Essential screenings and interventions by age:
                    <ul class="wellness-list">
                        <li>Bone density scans</li>
                        <li>Cancer screenings</li>
                        <li>Vision/hearing tests</li>
                        <li>Vaccination updates</li>
                    </ul>
                    Personalized prevention plans with healthcare providers optimize outcomes.
                    </p>
                </section>
            </div>
        </article>

        <section class="health-interaction">
            <h2>Aging Questions?</h2>
            <div class="query-container">
                <form action="/generate" method="POST">
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <textarea name="question" rows="4"
                            placeholder="Ask aging-related questions (e.g., 'Best exercises for osteoporosis prevention?')"
                            aria-label="Aging question input"></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">
                        Get Aging Insights
                    </button>
                </form>

                <% if (responseText) { %>
                    <div class="response-card">
                        <div class="response-content">
                            <%= responseText %>
                                <p class="medical-note">Consult your healthcare provider for personalized aging plans</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } %>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>
</body>
</html>